1. Loops
a) Whenever we have to perform some repetitive tasks
b) If you have group of something, and over that group you wish to perform some action/operation

1- while loop

   Variable;
   while(ConditionOverVariable)
   {
     This will execute only if condition is true;
     I/D;
   }

2- for loop
      for(Variable;ConditionOverVariable;I/D )
      {
        This will execute only if condition is true;
      }


